<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>About Storia</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@400;700&family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
</head>
<body>
  <div class="background-gradient"></div>
  <div class="grid-overlay"></div>

  <header class="main-header">
    <nav class="nav-container">
      <a href="/" class="logo">
        <img src="/assets/images/Storia-Logo.png" alt="Storia" class="logo-image">
      </a>
      <div class="nav-links">
        <a href="/books">Books</a>
        <% if (user) { %>
          <a href="/profile">Profile</a>
          <a href="/auth/logout">Logout</a>
        <% } else { %>
          <a href="/login">Login</a>
        <% } %>
        <a href="/about" class="active">About</a>
        <a href="/">Home</a>
      </div>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <main>
    <section class="about-section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-header">
          <h1>About Storia</h1>
          <p>Making literature accessible and enjoyable for everyone</p>
        </div>

        <div class="about-content">
          <div class="mission-card">
            <div class="icon-circle">
              <i class="fas fa-book-reader"></i>
            </div>
            <h2>Our Mission</h2>
            <p>Storia is an AI-powered platform designed to enhance reading experiences by creating custom soundtracks that align
              with the mood and plot of the book being read.
              What problem the project is solving:
              Storia addresses the issue of a disjointed and less engaging reading experience due to the ineffective selection of
              soundtracks for books. The platform aims to provide an immersive experience by seamlessly integrating audio that
              matches the narrative.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="features-grid">
            <div class="feature-card">
              <i class="fas fa-music"></i>
              <h3>Immersive Audio</h3>
              <p>Experience books with AI-generated ambient music that adapts to the story's mood.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
              <i class="fas fa-mobile-alt"></i>
              <h3>Read Anywhere</h3>
              <p>Access your books on any device with our responsive design and offline support.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
              <i class="fas fa-eye"></i>
              <h3>Focus Mode</h3>
              <p>Minimize distractions with our enhanced focus mode for concentrated reading.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
              <i class="fas fa-download"></i>
              <h3>Multiple Formats</h3>
              <p>Download books in various formats including EPUB, PDF, and Kindle.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="faq-section">
            <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
            <div class="faq-grid">
              <div class="faq-item">
                <h3>Is Storia free to use?</h3>
                <p>Yes! Storia is completely free, powered by Project Gutenberg's extensive library of public domain books.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="faq-item">
                <h3>How does the music feature work?</h3>
                <p>Our AI analyzes the mood and context of each page to generate appropriate background music that enhances your reading experience.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="faq-item">
                <h3>Can I read books offline?</h3>
                <p>Yes, you can download books in various formats for offline reading on your preferred device.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="faq-item">
                <h3>What books are available?</h3>
                <p>We offer thousands of classic books from Project Gutenberg's collection, including literature, philosophy, science, and more.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="faq-item">
                <h3>How do I customize my reading experience?</h3>
                <p>Storia offers various customization options including font size adjustment, focus mode, and theme settings.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="faq-item">
                <h3>Is there a mobile app?</h3>
                <p>Currently, Storia is available as a web application optimized for all devices. A dedicated mobile app is in development.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer>
    <div class="container">
      <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Storia. Powered by Project Gutenberg.</p>
    </div>
  </footer>
</body>
</html> 